import { Button, Col, Form, Row } from "react-bootstrap";

const FormInput = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Row>
                <Form>
                    <Col sm="5">
                        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="ادخل السؤال " />
                    </Col>
                    <Col sm="5">
                        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="ادخل الاجابة " />
                    </Col>
                    <Col sm="5">
                    <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
                        اضافة
                    </Button>
                    </Col>                </Form>
            </Row>
        </>
    )
}
export default FormInput;
